#: /KLib/ST_Klib.ST_Klib
msgctxt "ST_Klib,Build_CS_Core.Build_CS_Core_C.mDescription"
msgid "Stores hologram data and manages photon streams received from Scanners.\r\n\r\nItem data, building limit and storage size is limited by the installed number of FaxIt Disks.\r\n\r\nData throughput is limited in wireless mode. Connecting it to other FaxIT buildings with Data Cables increases throughput by 100%."
msgstr "Stores hologram data and manages photon streams received from Scanners.\r\n\r\nItem data, building limit and storage size is limited by the installed number of FaxIt Disks.\r\n\r\nData throughput is limited in wireless mode. Connecting it to other FaxIT buildings with Data Cables increases throughput by 100%."

