msgid "Collects air from the environment. The higher it is, the more air the Air Collector can collect.\r\n\r\nThe higher the elevation, the faster it can collect air.\r\n\r\nCollection speed will be reduced if other Air Collectors are nearby.  This range can be viewed with R (default) in build mode.\r\n\r\nIf placed nearly a Gas Pillar it will collect Toxic Air."
