msgid "Attached to the Modular Miner.\r\nIncreases Modular Miner power consumption.\r\nTough enough to mine any ore.\r\nStandard extraction rate: 120 / min per output.\r\n\r\nAll mining bonuses ('Mining Efficiency') are directly applied to the extraction rate of the miner.\r\nExample: 50% x 120 / min = 60 / min per output.\r\n\r\nNOTE: Node purity counts towards the mining bonus and NOT towards the base extraction rate."
