msgctxt "StringTable_KLib_Buildings,Build_Module_Fluid_D"
msgid "Attached to the Modular Miner.\r\nIncreases the power required by the Modular Miner.\r\n\r\nIncreases the Miner's Mining Efficiency based on the supplied fluid. Miner will not activate unless a fluid is supplied.\r\n\r\nBonus to Mining Efficiency can be viewed from inside the Miner Menu 'Fluid Info' panel."
