#: /KLib/StringTables/StringTable_KLib_Buildings.StringTable_KLib_Buildings
msgctxt "StringTable_KLib_Buildings,Build_OreWascher_D"
msgid "Purifies loose materials through industrial washing with a fluid. Outputs unwanted byproducts (like gangue) as a liquid slurry.\r\n\r\nHead Lift: 10 meters.\r\n(Allows fluids to be transported 10 meters upwards.)\r\n\r\nContains both Conveyor Belt and Pipeline input and output ports."
msgstr "Purifies loose materials through industrial washing with a fluid. Outputs unwanted byproducts (like gangue) as a liquid slurry.\r\n\r\nHead Lift: 10 meters.\r\n(Allows fluids to be transported 10 meters upwards.)\r\n\r\nContains both Conveyor Belt and Pipeline input and output ports."

