#. Key:	FluidConditioner_D
#. SourceLocation:	/KLib/StringTables/StringTable_KLib_Buildings.StringTable_KLib_Buildings
#: /KLib/StringTables/StringTable_KLib_Buildings.StringTable_KLib_Buildings
msgctxt "StringTable_KLib_Buildings,FluidConditioner_D"
msgid "Processes fluids by reducing them to solid components or treating them with a selected filter.\r\nEvery slot has its own production time.\r\n\r\nHead Lift: 10 meters. (Allows fluids to be transported 10 meters upwards.)\r\n\r\nHas a single belt output which outputs the solid products in a set order.\r\n\r\nThis fixed output order can be sorted with splitter trees or a smart sorting system."
msgstr "Processes fluids by reducing them to solid components or treating them with a selected filter.\r\nEvery slot has its own production time.\r\n\r\nHead Lift: 10 meters. (Allows fluids to be transported 10 meters upwards.)\r\n\r\nHas a single belt output which outputs the solid products in a set order.\r\n\r\nThis fixed output order can be sorted with splitter trees or a smart sorting system."

